"BONE LACING"

This cyberware surgery covers the users bones in a durable material, granting
many improvements depending on the material used.

Plastic grants +1 Body, and +2 Strength in unarmed combat.

Aluminium grants +1 Body, +1 Impact Armour and +3 Strengtt in unarmed combat.

Ceramic grants +1 Body, +2 Impact Armour and +3 Stength in unarmed combat.

Kevlar grants +1 Body and +1 Ballistic Armour.

Titanium grants +2 Body, +1 Ballistic Armour, +1 Impact armour and +4 Strength to unarmed combat.
